<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٧٢:</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ <span class="c3">{لِلَّذِينَ أَحْسَنُوا الحُسْنَى}</span>: مِثْلُهَا حُسْنَى.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{وَزِيَادَةٌ}</span>: مَغْفِرَةٌ وَرِضْوَانٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> النَّظَرُ إِلَى وَجْهِهِ - عز وجل -.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الكِبْرِيَاءُ:</span> المُلْكُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>